message: v0.1.4 add the hidden and animated properties to the NavigationBar
add Drawer component, add some props to SegmentedBar
Fix PropTypes and React.createClass deprecation changes in React 16
fix "big icon button" bug on Android, #44
Refactor AlbumView, fix a bug in TransformView, #52

Use 'react-native-deprecated-custom-components' from master

Someone has fixed issue of using `React.PropTypes` (https://github.com/facebookarchive/react-native-custom-components/pull/11)
But they have not yet published that fix to npm repo

For temporary workaround, use 'react-native-deprecated-custom-components' from master
Support custom width for the indicator of SegmentedBar
Support rn 0.56, add PureComponent container for TopView, #259, #260, #263, #264
Remove all buildProps functions, support rn 0.58, up to 0.6.0
support rn0.61.4; change react-native-deprecated-custom-components to react-native-legacy-components
